         <p class="mt-2 text-base leading-7">The <span class="font-bold">attached ticket</span> will get you into the conference for three days of workshops and talks from some of the best builders and thinkers in the bitcoin L2 space. You'll need it to check-in!</p>
	  <p class="mt-2 text-base leading-7">If you still need a place to stay, we've got a short <a href="https://btcpp.dev#venue" target="_blank" class="font-semibold underline underline-offset-4">list of suggestions on the conference website</a>; I'd also really recommend the Hyatt which is pricey but a nice walk to the venue. Any hotel downtown should be great, or an Airbnb nearby.</p>
